Class ObjectivePairingService

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.atakmap.android.routes.nav.ObjectivePairingService
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    RouteNavigationManager.RouteNavigationManagerEventListener, RouteNavigator.RouteNavigatorListener

    public class ObjectivePairingService
extends java.lang.Object
implements RouteNavigator.RouteNavigatorListener, RouteNavigationManager.RouteNavigationManagerEventListener
    This class is responsible for drawing a line from the user to their current objective.
